msgctxt "an4.71:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4 "
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4 "

#. HTML: </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.71:0.2"
msgid "8. Apaṇṇakavagga "
msgstr "8. Guaranteed "

#. HTML: </p><h1>
#. VAR: padhāna-apaṇṇakapaṭipadāsuttaṃ (bj)
msgctxt "an4.71:0.3"
msgid "71. Padhānasutta "
msgstr "71. Effort "

#. HTML: </h1></div><p>
#. REF: sc1
msgctxt "an4.71:1.1"
msgid "“Catūhi, bhikkhave, dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu apaṇṇakappaṭipadaṃ paṭipanno hoti, yoni cassa āraddhā hoti āsavānaṃ khayāya. "
msgstr "“Mendicants, when a mendicant has four things their practice is guaranteed, and they have laid the groundwork for ending the defilements. "

msgctxt "an4.71:1.2"
msgid "Katamehi catūhi? "
msgstr "What four? "

msgctxt "an4.71:1.3"
msgid "Idha, bhikkhave, bhikkhu sīlavā hoti, bahussuto hoti, āraddhavīriyo hoti, paññavā hoti. "
msgstr "It’s when a mendicant is ethical, learned, energetic, and wise. "

msgctxt "an4.71:1.4"
msgid "Imehi kho, bhikkhave, catūhi dhammehi samannāgato bhikkhu apaṇṇakappaṭipadaṃ paṭipanno hoti, yoni cassa āraddhā hoti āsavānaṃ khayāyā”ti. "
msgstr "When a mendicant has these four things their practice is guaranteed, and they have laid the groundwork for ending the defilements.” "

#. HTML: </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.71:1.5"
msgid "Paṭhamaṃ. "
msgstr ""

